@*FAQ Section*@
<!-- FAQ Section -->
<div id="faq" class="faq-section mb-3">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-8 text-center">
                <span class="section-subtitle">FAQ</span>
                <h2 class="section-title gradient-text">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
                    <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
                    <div class="accordion-item glass-card">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq1">
                                How long does the beginner's course take to complete?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="faq1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                Our beginner's course typically takes 30 hours to complete. This includes both theoretical and practical modules. You can complete the course at your own pace within a 3-month access period.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
                    <div class="accordion-item glass-card">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq2">
                                Are your courses certified?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="faq2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                Yes, all our courses are certified by the State Department of Motor Vehicles and meet all required educational standards for driver training. Upon completion, you'll receive an official certificate.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
                    <div class="accordion-item glass-card">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq3">
                                Can I access the course materials on my mobile device?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="faq3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                Yes, our platform is fully responsive and works on all devices including smartphones, tablets, and computers. You can switch between devices seamlessly while maintaining your progress.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
                    <div class="accordion-item glass-card">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq4">
                                What payment methods do you accept?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="faq4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                We accept all major credit cards, debit cards, and PayPal. We also offer flexible payment plans to make our courses more accessible. Contact us for more information about payment options.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
                    <div class="accordion-item glass-card">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq5">
                                How soon can I start after enrolling?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="faq5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                You can start immediately after enrolling! Once your payment is processed, you'll receive instant access to all course materials and can begin your learning journey right away.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- FAQ Item 6 -->
                    <div class="accordion-item glass-card">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq6">
                                What happens if I don't pass the final test?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="faq6" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                Don't worry! You can retake the final test up to three times at no additional cost. We also provide additional study materials and support to help you succeed. Our instructors are always available to help you understand any challenging topics.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

